Kansal Enterprises® — B2B specialists in decorative metal manufacturing for over 36 years. Trusted by global brands for our craftsmanship and scale.

Meet Kansal Enterprises

We’re Kansal Enterprises a modern metal decor manufacturer with roots going back to 1989. Based in Moradabad, we’ve spent over 35 years perfecting the art of handcrafted design across home, garden, kitchen, and seasonal decor. From traditional techniques to cutting-edge finishes like UV printing and copper flaming, everything we make is built in-house for quality and consistency.

Get in touch

Get in touch

Bringing Ideas to Life

At Kansal Enterprises, we specialize in transforming design concepts into striking metal decor. From precision-cut products to detailed surface finishes, our work is crafted to tell a story through form, texture, and craftsmanship.

Collaborate with us

Let’s create something extraordinary together. Whether you’re looking for custom metal decor, precision-crafted products, or unique finishes, Kansal Enterprises is here to bring your ideas to life with care and craftsmanship.

01
Design with Purpose

At Kansal, every product starts with intention crafted to balance form and function. From garden decor to festive accents, we design pieces that are as useful as they are beautiful.

02
Rooted in Craft

We partner with skilled artisans who bring decades of expertise to the table. Their hands shape each item with care, turning raw metal into meaningful decor.
